name: Lyndsey DeMoss
email: Despite extensive searching of the Edge Academy website (edge4kids.org), including the "Meet the Team" and "Board Members" pages, and reviewing annual reports, a direct email address for Lyndsey DeMoss, Dean of Students at Edge Academy, could not be found. While the domain @edge4kids.org is used for other staff members (e.g., board members), no email address following a similar pattern was explicitly listed for Lyndsey DeMoss. Third-party sites provided personal email addresses (ldemoss116@aol.com, lynsdemoss116@yahoo.com) and phone numbers, but these are not official Edge Academy contact details and are not suitable for this request. Therefore, an official email address for Lyndsey DeMoss at Edge Academy could not be found.
